content: I think the Gyeonggi building is a special visit The palace is so beautiful and gorgeous. Of course, the meaning is a little worse than Gyeonggi Palace (in my opinion), but the gorgeousness is better. The experience is fantastic!
Summer Seonggok Art Museum ㅎㅎ The atmosphere of summer is so good ㅎ I really like it. Listen to the sound of birds in the shade of trees ㅎㅎ It's like a really pretty place in summer!
